# REQUIREMENTS

@node requirements "Requirements"
DMA requires :

  - Kick 2.04 at least
      (that's beacause 1.3 is obsolete :) 

  - Patience
      (that's because it's less-than-one version :)

  - Amiga 4000/40 50MHz with Cyberstorm (68060) accelerator, 32M memory
      (not really, just a silly joke *sigh*)

Also  one  is  advised to posess Advanced Dungeons & Dragons ® Roleplaying
System.  (Version at least 1.0 (prefered 2.0))

How-To-Install :

  - Oh, just put DMA icon (or file, if you still prefer Shell than WB :)
    wherever you want and launch it !  Put docs in your docs directory or
    wherever.

  - DMA archive should contains:

    . DMA  (Main proggy)
    . DMA.info  (I would be pleased if you'll send me REAL icon for DMA
                (preferably in MugicWB style, but other may do) :)
    . DMA/Mods/PotionGen  (Potion Generator Module <- should always be here!)
    . DMA/Mods/CharGen    (Char Generator Module <- should always be here!)
    . DMA/Mods/Prefs      (Preferences Edit Module <- should always be here!)
    . DMA/Docs/DMA.guide  (DMA  docs  in  AmigaGuide®  format (you're reading
                                                               this))
    . DMA/Docs/DMA.guide.info (*grin*)
    . DMA/Docs.info
    . DMA/libs/reqtools.library (The best  shared  library  ever  created  by
                             human being ;-[ <-- womphyric grin)

Tested on :

  - A500 68000 Kick 2.04 WB 2.1 .5M Chip 2.5M Slow 85HD
      (created on that junk :)
  - I'm in desperate need of Beta-Testors
@endnode

