# INFO

@node info "Info"
  Well, Dungeon Master Aid is a program considered to be a help in several
situations  which  may  happen during your play session.  It may help when
your   dices  are  hopelessly  lost  under  the  cupboard,  or  when  your
Greatest-Medieval-Scottish-Songs CD is actually lended, or when you're too
tired  to  think  about  weather.   (The  last one is only when you're not
english man.) It can also do other useless things - see @{" Main Help " link help}.
@endnode

